==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|transliteratus|lang=la}} past participle of {{term|transliterare||to transliterate|lang=la}}, from {{term|trans-||across|lang=la}} + {{term|littera||letter|lang=la}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{linguistics}} The act or product of [[transliterating]], or of representing [[letter]]s or [[word]]s in the [[character]]s of another [[alphabet]] or [[script]].

